11#include "media/base/rid_description.h"
12
13namespace cricket {
14
15RidDescription::RidDescription() = default;
16RidDescription::RidDescription(const std::string& rid, RidDirection direction)
17 : rid{rid}, direction{direction} {}
18RidDescription::RidDescription(const RidDescription& other) = default;
19RidDescription::~RidDescription() = default;
20RidDescription& RidDescription::operator=(const RidDescription& other) =
21 default;
22bool RidDescription::operator==(const RidDescription& other) const {
23 return rid == other.rid && direction == other.direction &&
24 payload_types == other.payload_types &&
25 restrictions == other.restrictions;
26}
27
28} // namespace cricket
